  <body>
    <p>&emsp; Scratchers are magic creatures that are a "mix" between cats and dogs. Scratchers are usually based around a civilization in the middle of the forest. They usually hunt for themselves unless they are below ten. Their strength and regeneration exceeds the normal mortal possabilitys. Some scientists seek this power.</p>
